<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #ebebeb;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #390101;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5e3023, #4a1506);
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .code-box {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4a1506;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 20px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 0px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #c08552;
            color: #390101;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #a56d42;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #c08552;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #390101;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
  <br><br>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            Password Reset
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password. Please use the verification code below to proceed:</p>
            <div class="code-box">{{code}}</div>
            <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have any concerns.</p>
            <p>Best regards, <br><strong>{{company}}</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2025 {{company}}. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
    <br><br>
</body>
</html>
